<h2 id="comments">Comments</h2>

<div id="c4696">

<p>That&#8217;s not stuck. If that&#8217;s how it is, that&#8217;s how it is.</p>

<p>If you don&#8217;t feel anything, well - so what? Don&#8217;t worry. Don&#8217;t pursue it if it makes you feel uncomfortable.</p>

